@startuml
    classDiagram
        [Root] SystemRequirement
        [SystemRequirement] Root

        SystemRequirement --> Root (requirement)
        Root --> SystemRequirement (requirement)

        [User] User
        [User] User --> Root (user)

        [DataModel] DataModel
        [DataModel] DataModel --> SystemRequirement (data model)

        [Service] Service
        [Service] Service --> Root (service)

        [Service] Service --> DataModel (service data model)

        [BusinessProcess] BusinessProcess
        [BusinessProcess] BusinessProcess --> Service (business process)

        [PresentationLayer] PresentationLayer
        [PresentationLayer] PresentationLayer --> Service (presentation layer service)

        [UI] UI
        [UI] UI --> PresentationLayer (UI layer)

        [Database] Database
        [Database] Database --> DataModel (database model)

        [SecurityLayer] SecurityLayer
        [SecurityLayer] SecurityLayer --> Database (security layer database)

        [ApplicationLayer] ApplicationLayer
        [ApplicationLayer] ApplicationLayer --> Service (application layer service)

        [Deployment] Deployment
        [Deployment] Deployment --> SystemRequirement (deployment requirement)

        [Testing] Testing
        [Testing] Testing --> BusinessProcess (testing business process)

        [Configuration] Configuration
        [Configuration] Configuration --> SystemRequirement (configuration requirement)

        [Maintenance] Maintenance
        [Maintenance] Maintenance --> BusinessProcess (maintenance business process)

        [Support] Support
        [Support] Support --> SystemRequirement (support requirement)

        [Documentation] Documentation
        [Documentation] Documentation --> SystemRequirement (documentation requirement)

        [Administration] Administration
        [Administration] Administration --> SystemRequirement (administration requirement)

        [Integration] Integration
        [Integration] Integration --> Service (integration service)

        [API] API
        [API] API --> Service (API service)

        [TestSuite] TestSuite
        [TestSuite] TestSuite --> Testing (test suite)

        [CodeReview] CodeReview
        [CodeReview] CodeReview --> BusinessProcess (code review process)

        [ReleaseNote] ReleaseNote
        [ReleaseNote] ReleaseNote --> SystemRequirement (release note requirement)

        [DeploymentPlan] DeploymentPlan
        [DeploymentPlan] DeploymentPlan --> Deployment (deployment plan)

        [Performance] Performance
        [Performance] Performance --> BusinessProcess (performance process)

        [Monitoring] Monitoring
        [Monitoring] Monitoring --> BusinessProcess (monitoring process)

        [Reporting] Reporting
        [Reporting] Reporting --> BusinessProcess (reporting process)

        [AccessControl] AccessControl
        [AccessControl] AccessControl --> SecurityLayer (access control layer)

        [Logging] Logging
        [Logging] Logging --> Database (logging layer)

@enduml
